Fwho is a basic fighter command. It allows you to see all the current
fighters on Darkwind. It also allows you to see some information about
your fellow fighters as listed below:

F = fighter is currently fighting.
I = fighter is currently reading or writing.
M = fighter is currently muffing the fighter line.
E = fighter wiz is editing.
[idle] = fighter is currently idle.

Syntax is: fwho
